## 2. Reflection: Mock Interview Experience
**Situation:** The assessment required the inclusion of a mock interview video to showcase work readiness.

**Task:** I needed to record a professional interview and then embed this multimedia artefact into my digital portfolio using Markdown or HTML.

**Action:** I prepared for common IT-related interview questions, recorded the session, and uploaded the file to a accessible PLATFORM. I then used an HTML embed code within my README to ensure the video was playable directly from the portfolio page.

**Result:** Successfully embedding the video demonstrated my ability to integrate multimedia elements into a technical project. It also allowed me to critically review my communication skills for future employment.

